":"夏天為大地帶來雨水<br />\n出街記得帶遮"},{"pid":"ef891e47da739c59c1e7fdd4f860d7443a97548b","tid":1991927,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798235c0414fe9a3c6001997fc8236b700b5ff59","tid":1991927,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947c77262a9940bbe68567a46cfbbe00cb8082fc","tid":1991927,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:24:17.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1be28ccd23e7aee2869563e5873b795f34c5620f","tid":1991927,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"#admin有話兒 <br />\n<br />\n所有手足都想遍地開花，不斷想快啲有新活動，亦好想圓星期日嘅唱歌心願。不過，每一次活動都有風險同對運動有長遠影響，所以每籌備一個活動(唔計大型集會)最少要諗好以下3件事:<br />\n1. 主題/目的<br />\n2. 安排足夠哨兵<br />\n3. 宣傳所需時間<br />\n<br />\n若然未夠時間宣傳及人力物力去盡力保障所有參加者嘅安全，同埋冇宏觀地考慮清楚各區活動嘅整體佈局，不但會增加手足嘅被捕風險，仲會影響到運動係咪可以長時間持續落去。因此本channel絕不鼓勵未有周詳計劃就即興搞任何活動。<br />\n<br />\n星星之火可以燎原。真心希望各手足毋忘初衷，切勿輕舉妄動，犠牲其他人嘅安全；咁樣運動先可以延續下去。<br />\n<br />\n5DN1L&middot;HK 中環移動<br />\n@Central_5DN1L_HK"},{"pid":"916152255a2910023baf890d8a7335dcaed39ee9","tid":1991927,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01cd2bfb0b5a999fbb41d66417d3256b7624fee","tid":1991927,"uid":220113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:09:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a2e895c161d16a40a42602545f3b106b9c97a0d","tid":1991927,"uid":165619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adaefed2a3360e77a72115f5cec0e3d3d634245f","tid":1991927,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T21:55:21.000Z","msg":"sorry為咗吸引大家入嚟 用咗個content farm方式標題<br />\n<br />\n其實我主要想同大家講 「落雨，開遮」 比你想像中更有用 <br />\n如果tldr可以拉到最底<br />\n<br />\n遮 喺香港抗爭當中有好多作用 <br />\n<br />\n一 可以擋子彈<br />\n二 可以用作自衛 (總比手無寸鐵好）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">三 就係可以用嚟cover手足</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n咁多個月以嚟大家都知道見到狗錄你影嘅時候要開遮<br />\n當手足做嘢 (無論換衫 裝修 私鳥）嘅時候要開遮<br />\n<em><ins>但係普遍人淨係記得&quot;行動中&quot;開遮<br />\n忽略咗&quot;離場&quot;都要開遮</ins></em><br />\n<br />\n好簡單舉例子(以下圖片都係google是但揾)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2P6Nk05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2P6Nk05.jpg&h=a3bdc0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sm9jb7N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsm9jb7N.jpg&h=12c1f3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你會見到<strong>手足嘅身高 服飾 髮型 裝備 打扮特徵全部都已經被影低晒 </strong><br />\n咁班狗就可以透過cctv揾番呢一身打扮嘅人 <br />\n<strong>由邊度出現 活動完咗之後去邊 搭咩車走等等</strong><br />\n<br />\n所以點解好多人打完狗/ 裝修完/ 魔法完 過咗2-3個月 就會比狗上門咬 <br />\n<em><ins>因為佢哋可以睇幾百上千個鐘片</ins></em> 為咗咬你呢位「極端核心激進勇武分子」<br />\n<br />\n但係如果手足行動嗰陣 有真係落雨開遮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLpZWBo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLpZWBo.jpg&h=00794153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似平時旁聽師咁cover手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>然後手足行動完嘅時候有人群遮陣掩護佢走<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60ndgBq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60ndgBq.jpg&h=8318a9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似咁樣 講真你唔會揾得番到底係邊個人落手<br />\n<br />\n所以想呼籲大家 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">無論乜人都好 出街一定要帶把遮</span></strong><br />\n無論長遮又好 縮骨遮都好<br />\n當有手足做嘢 唔好成碌木咁企喺度/打卡拍片<br />\n你同身邊嘅人一齊開遮行過去 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">掩護手足行動 <br />\n掩護手足退場</span></strong><br />\n務求令手足盡量唔好落入cctv/ 鏡頭之下<br />\n<br />\n唔好再好似以前咁淨係鳩叫完開遮<br />\n又遮唔到手足 行動完又唔掩護手足離場<br />\n咁樣開遮係無能用的<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我心目中理想嘅狀況話</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 人要夠多 (最好full blackbloc)</span></strong><br />\n2. 手足行動嘅時候幫手開遮cover<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 手足行動完 遮陣照包圍到手足 然後手足融入番遊行大部隊/ 一齊開遮融入遮陣之後離開</span><br />\n<em><ins>(我個人覺得離場最重要 就算入場/郁手嗰陣入咗鏡 但唔知手足之後走去邊的話 理論上都好難揾得番手足）</ins></em><br />\n4. 然後收遮 咁手足嘅特徵最可能被保護得到 班狗都好難追番cctv<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論下點做會更好<br />\n但我覺得遮陣保護手足係必須"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:14:27.000Z","msg":"有用Post 一定要推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n係我地呢一代一輩子嘅責任"},{"pid":"660f58d3f10af9d605bd94daa0ceac0888259785","tid":1991927,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2e06b6012f25eb9f7e36ec98bb3aa21a4aff4cb","tid":1991927,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:32:00.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"4b24bf228035d075591aec9680780e5cf85f9e2b","tid":1991927,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:34:16.000Z","msg":"遮陣真係基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463a2b1dac97f39c63fd7e091e0f508382ae132c","tid":1991927,"uid":7137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73c8ad952d248de4d2d6629934e0724926820fb5","tid":1991927,"uid":209644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:49:25.000Z","msg":"好清楚 一於照做 thx"},{"pid":"11a98aaf005fba33949cafd54280599adc265d08","tid":1991927,"uid":164079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6124b64b62ee3878311bf437abae4045b3e05196","tid":1991927,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T18:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fecbb2b2d515ec5093186e9fea951