e8ea45301dcf090cd8","tid":1991927,"uid":3705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T21:09:06.000Z","msg":"Cover退場真係好重要<br />\n推"},{"pid":"09fdd09ec402942b817bbd3be6165e6d82c354e4","tid":1991927,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f364b280f102ce82e3fa559f9d3a9c1bcd780e84","tid":1991927,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:45:23.000Z","msg":"落雨同出太陽都可以用遮架啦"},{"pid":"2600363a82d8f59f9d92e77529dfeadd2eb2f59b","tid":1991927,"uid":238920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"開遮遮手足,同時亦都要遮埋自己<br />\n有案例係個手足俾人告暴動,幫佢遮果個因為協助一齊告埋暴動"},{"pid":"c567ec0a5ffe96051b5292d7c12f2245277c4963","tid":1991927,"uid":357332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adaefed2a3360e77a72115f5cec0e3d3d634245f","tid":1991927,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T21:55:21.000Z","msg":"sorry為咗吸引大家入嚟 用咗個content farm方式標題<br />\n<br />\n其實我主要想同大家講 「落雨，開遮」 比你想像中更有用 <br />\n如果tldr可以拉到最底<br />\n<br />\n遮 喺香港抗爭當中有好多作用 <br />\n<br />\n一 可以擋子彈<br />\n二 可以用作自衛 (總比手無寸鐵好）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">三 就係可以用嚟cover手足</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n咁多個月以嚟大家都知道見到狗錄你影嘅時候要開遮<br />\n當手足做嘢 (無論換衫 裝修 私鳥）嘅時候要開遮<br />\n<em><ins>但係普遍人淨係記得&quot;行動中&quot;開遮<br />\n忽略咗&quot;離場&quot;都要開遮</ins></em><br />\n<br />\n好簡單舉例子(以下圖片都係google是但揾)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2P6Nk05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2P6Nk05.jpg&h=a3bdc0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sm9jb7N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsm9jb7N.jpg&h=12c1f3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你會見到<strong>手足嘅身高 服飾 髮型 裝備 打扮特徵全部都已經被影低晒 </strong><br />\n咁班狗就可以透過cctv揾番呢一身打扮嘅人 <br />\n<strong>由邊度出現 活動完咗之後去邊 搭咩車走等等</strong><br />\n<br />\n所以點解好多人打完狗/ 裝修完/ 魔法完 過咗2-3個月 就會比狗上門咬 <br />\n<em><ins>因為佢哋可以睇幾百上千個鐘片</ins></em> 為咗咬你呢位「極端核心激進勇武分子」<br />\n<br />\n但係如果手足行動嗰陣 有真係落雨開遮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLpZWBo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLpZWBo.jpg&h=00794153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似平時旁聽師咁cover手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>然後手足行動完嘅時候有人群遮陣掩護佢走<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60ndgBq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60ndgBq.jpg&h=8318a9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似咁樣 講真你唔會揾得番到底係邊個人落手<br />\n<br />\n所以想呼籲大家 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">無論乜人都好 出街一定要帶把遮</span></strong><br />\n無論長遮又好 縮骨遮都好<br />\n當有手足做嘢 唔好成碌木咁企喺度/打卡拍片<br />\n你同身邊嘅人一齊開遮行過去 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">掩護手足行動 <br />\n掩護手足退場</span></strong><br />\n務求令手足盡量唔好落入cctv/ 鏡頭之下<br />\n<br />\n唔好再好似以前咁淨係鳩叫完開遮<br />\n又遮唔到手足 行動完又唔掩護手足離場<br />\n咁樣開遮係無能用的<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我心目中理想嘅狀況話</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 人要夠多 (最好full blackbloc)</span></strong><br />\n2. 手足行動嘅時候幫手開遮cover<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 手足行動完 遮陣照包圍到手足 然後手足融入番遊行大部隊/ 一齊開遮融入遮陣之後離開</span><br />\n<em><ins>(我個人覺得離場最重要 就算入場/郁手嗰陣入咗鏡 但唔知手足之後走去邊的話 理論上都好難揾得番手足）</ins></em><br />\n4. 然後收遮 咁手足嘅特徵最可能被保護得到 班狗都好難追番cctv<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論下點做會更好<br />\n但我覺得遮陣保護手足係必須"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2c93da65df0ad527b404cda03136aa3153851c","tid":1991927,"uid":242323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:24:05.000Z","msg":"非常認同<br />\n要推"},{"pid":"2ed249946ec0e0eae94f9b17c8e34ab96ee89ee5","tid":1991927,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc8d3d907eb07fd951eaa68f99dcd90e0a7ee66","tid":1991927,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"Agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c72b59eee1e61ea7adf06a2aa31e53236556c2","tid":1991927,"uid":146375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:38:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c34aa3916d366fef08259ef9e7ebdd5cd2a4a991","tid":1991927,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:56:27.000Z","msg":"十分同意 和理非做唔到其他都幫手cover"},{"pid":"e4da2daf3bf9e5da7a4254af987419043fcd53c6","tid":1991927,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ae1946b86565d53e701a77326c14da60972211","tid":1991927,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4da2daf3bf9e5da7a4254af987419043fcd53c6","tid":1991927,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3c938b9ee110ff38ebd04c7878ff0edeb61f28","tid":1991927,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7ae1946b86565d53e701a77326c14da60972211","tid":1991927,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4da2daf3bf9e5da7a4254af987419043fcd53c6","tid":1991927,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB